up for her that way.

1224
01:44:13,286 --> 01:44:15,356
My wife and l are separated.

1225
01:44:17,806 --> 01:44:19,034
Yes.

1226
01:44:19,286 --> 01:44:20,639
Yes!

1227
01:44:24,126 --> 01:44:25,275
l..

1228
01:44:26,366 --> 01:44:30,359
l thought l could face what we had
to go through after we were married.

1229
01:44:32,166 --> 01:44:33,645
l couldn't.

1230
01:44:35,046 --> 01:44:37,196
l wasn't ready to give
up my position..

1231
01:44:37,286 --> 01:44:39,720
..because of my employer's
prejudices.

1232
01:44:40,886 --> 01:44:43,639
My family talked to me about it.

1233
01:44:44,046 --> 01:44:45,365
My friends.

1234
01:44:49,646 --> 01:44:51,364
My dear friends.

1235
01:44:52,646 --> 01:44:54,125
So l panicked.

1236
01:44:55,206 --> 01:44:56,559
Panicked!

1237
01:44:57,966 --> 01:45:01,038
l asked my firm to transfer
me to Mexico.

1238
01:45:03,446 --> 01:45:06,358
And you'll never believe what l did.

1239
01:45:07,726 --> 01:45:09,364
l wrote a letter.

1240
01:45:11,806 --> 01:45:13,364
Dear Marianne:

1241
01:45:14,446 --> 01:45:19,566
