me everywhere.

1244
01:45:37,766 --> 01:45:39,722
Now l'm going back.

1245
01:45:42,886 --> 01:45:44,717
l don't even know where she is.

1246
01:45:47,726 --> 01:45:49,364
But l've got to find her.

1247
01:45:51,206 --> 01:45:54,118
Plead with her to understand.

1248
01:45:58,646 --> 01:45:59,965
To forgive me.

1249
01:46:02,446 --> 01:46:06,280
lf she cares for you,
she'll understand.

1250
01:46:08,286 --> 01:46:09,639
Don't you see?

1251
01:46:10,766 --> 01:46:14,884
Even if she does, l know
l'll never forget.

1252
01:46:18,206 --> 01:46:19,878
l wrote that letter.

1253
01:46:24,126 --> 01:46:25,957
Listen to that music, Glocken.

1254
