01:50:02,206 --> 01:50:03,355
Come in.

1304
01:50:07,206 --> 01:50:08,559
l have money.

1305
01:50:16,446 --> 01:50:17,720
Come here.

1306
01:50:18,366 --> 01:50:19,640
