01:54:38,726 --> 01:54:40,205
l never knew what people
meant by that word.

1332
01:54:40,286 --> 01:54:42,720
Say, don't say it. l can't
bear the sound of it.

1333
01:54:42,886 --> 01:54:45,958
Then why did you lead
me on during the trip?

1334
01:54:47,766 --> 01:54:50,883
You never considered my
feelings at all, did you?

1335
01:54:52,206 --> 01:54:53,639
No.

1336
01:54:54,566 --> 01:54:55,965
And l'm sorry for that.

1337
01:54:57,286 --> 01:55:01,723
Mrs. Treadwell, l'm only a third-grade
officer on a second-rate ship.

1338
01:55:01,806 --> 01:55:04,195
But it has given me an opportunity
to observe people.

1339
01:55:04,286 --> 01:55:06,561
l've seen women like you before.

1340
01:55:06,646 --> 01:55:09,956
Forty-six-year-old women
who are still coquettes.

1341
01:55:10,046 --> 01:55:13,721
They travel on boats often. Always
searching for something.

1342
01:55:14,046 --> 01:55:16,116
Do you know where that searching
ends Mrs. Treadwell?

1343
01:55:16,206 --> 01:55:19,198
lt ends by sitting in a nightclub
with a paid escort..

1344
01:55:19,286 --> 01:55:21,356
..who tells you the
lies you must hear.

1345
01:55:24,166 --> 01:55:27,636
You are a most mundane,
ordinary man.

1346
01:55:30,766 --> 01:55:33,360
How extraordinary that
a man like you..

1347
01:55:33,646 --> 01:55:36,160
..should be saying things
like this to me.

1348
01:55:40,726 --> 01:55:41,954
Probably true.

1349
01:55:48,886 --> 01:55:52,196
l think this evening's festivities
have come to an end.

1350
01:55:54,886 --> 01:55:58,356
- l shall be happy to see you to
your door. - lt's quite unnecessary.

1351
01:56:00,126 --> 01:56:01,718
l'll find my own way.

1352
01:56:34,046 --> 01:56:36,116
- Darling? - Yeah Leiben.

1353
01:56:36,206 --> 01:56:39,198
l didn't know there
was a Frau Rieber.

1354
01:56:41,206 --> 01:56:43,356
What do you mean, a Frau Rieber?

1355
01:56:43,446 --> 01:56:46,643
The purser told me you sent
a cable to Frankfurt..

1356
01:56:46,726 --> 01:56:48,956
..addressed to a Frau Rieber.

1357
01:56:49,566 --> 01:56:52,717
l did not mention it before, because
l could not bear the humiliation.

1358
01:56:52,806 --> 01:56:56,162
lt is the tragedy of my life.
She will not let me go.

1359
01:56:56,246 --> 01:56:58,714
l must go on supporting her
and the three children.

1360
01:56:58,806 --> 01:57:00,717
There are three children?

1361
01:57:00,966 --> 01:57:02,558
Well they have no understanding
of me.

1362
01:57:02,646 --> 01:57:04,125
And l have no understanding of them.

1363
01:57:04,206 --> 01:57:08,358
They hang on. They hang on. They
suck the life's blood out of me.

1364
01:57:08,446 --> 01:57:10,641
They will not let go.
They will not let go.

1365
01:57:10,886 --> 01:57:13,639
l am a vital, passionate man.

1366
01:57:13,766 --> 01:57:17,202
l need love. l must have love.

1367
01:57:17,646 --> 01:57:21,559
Say you understand.
You must understand.

1368
01:57:21,646 --> 01:57:23,204
l understand.

1369
