and you've fallen for it.

1395
02:01:02,206 --> 02:01:06,165
My god. l can see it if you can't.
She wants her precious needle.

1396
02:01:06,246 --> 02:01:08,555
- She doesn't want you.
- This may be true.

1397
02:01:09,566 --> 02:01:11,045
lf this is true..

1398
02:01:14,886 --> 02:01:18,117
When l had my heart attack,
there was a dream l had.

1399
02:01:19,206 --> 02:01:22,960
You can talk about death. l've
seen it many times as a doctor.

1400
02:01:23,886 --> 02:01:26,958
But you never know what it's like
until it almost happens to you.

1401
02:01:31,566 --> 02:01:33,796
l dreamed l had already died.

1402
02:01:35,366 --> 02:01:39,041
l dreamed l was in a box. The sweat
broke out all over my body.

1403
02:01:40,726 --> 02:01:45,197
l wanted to cry out, l can't
be dead, l haven't lived!

1404
02:01:47,886 --> 02:01:49,035
Who has?

1405
02:01:50,726 --> 02:01:53,115
Do you think this woman
is the answer, Willie?

1406
02:01:53,286 --> 02:01:56,278
A woman like this. All
she's been through.

1407
02:01:56,366 --> 02:01:59,358
She has seen everything. There
are no surprises left for her.

1408
02:02:01,726 --> 02:02:07,198
Even if it's love, Willie, l hope we
can deny the myth that love lasts.

1409
02:02:17,806 --> 02:02:21,355
You are not young, Mrs. Treadwell.

1410
02:02:22,566 --> 02:02:26,036
