1411
02:02:32,646 --> 02:02:37,640
Behind those old eyes, you
hide a 16-year-old heart.

1412
02:02:39,126 --> 02:02:40,639
Poor fool.

1413
02:02:45,966 --> 02:02:49,356
ls that what men really
find attractive?

1414
02:03:11,206 --> 02:03:12,559
Baby..

1415
02:03:14,286 --> 02:03:17,164
You just haven't managed to grow up.

1416
02:03:18,046 --> 02:03:23,359
Mrs. Treadwell of Murray
Hill, Virginia.

1417
02:03:25,646 --> 02:03:26,965
Now!

1418
02:03:29,286 --> 02:03:31,880
You can paint your toenails green.

1419
02:03:38,206 --> 02:03:40,720
