1420
02:03:43,206 --> 02:03:44,639
Alone.

1421
02:03:47,126 --> 02:03:48,718
Sitting in a cafe..

1422
02:03:50,286 --> 02:03:52,641
..with a paid escort.

1423
02:04:13,806 --> 02:04:15,034
Let me go.

1424
02:04:16,646 --> 02:04:17,965
Let me go.

1425
02:04:29,806 --> 02:04:31,364
Mrs. Treadwell.

1426
02:04:33,806 --> 02:04:38,721
Excuse me. That greaser told
me Cabin 14. Excuse me.

1427
02:04:39,566 --> 02:04:40,965
Excuse me.

1428
02:04:41,886 --> 02:04:43,035
Get out!

1429
02:04:44,366 --> 02:04:45,640
Get out!

1430
02:04:50,126 --> 02:04:51,559
Get out!

1431
02:04:52,806 --> 02:04:55,559
You know l'm sorry, l truly am
sorry. l didn't know it l was just..

1432
02:04:55,646 --> 02:04:58,114
- Pig! - Hey, what the hell?

1433
02:04:58,206 --> 02:05:02,165
Go on. Get out. Get out. Get out!

