1442
02:06:17,286 --> 02:06:18,639
Tell me.

1443
02:06:26,206 --> 02:06:27,639
Promise you won't laugh.

1444
02:06:28,966 --> 02:06:30,115
l won't laugh.

1445
02:06:32,646 --> 02:06:34,637
lt's something l saw the
time l went to Taxco.

1446
02:06:34,726 --> 02:06:36,876
lt was just a flash passing
