1447
02:06:37,366 --> 02:06:40,119
lt was a man and a woman. A crowd
had gathered around them.

1448
02:06:40,206 --> 02:06:43,721
They were staggering and swaying.
l thought they were dancing.

1449
02:06:45,046 --> 02:06:48,038
The man had his hand raised and
there was a long knife in it.

1450
02:06:48,206 --> 02:06:51,198
The woman's breast and
stomach were pierced.

1451
02:06:51,286 --> 02:06:53,720
