She was beating him with a stone.

1453
02:06:59,886 --> 02:07:02,719
l'll never forget the
look on their faces.

1454
02:07:04,206 --> 02:07:05,958
lt wasn't all hatred.

1455
02:07:06,366 --> 02:07:11,281
lt was like there was some great
bond between them in that hatred.

1456
02:07:13,966 --> 02:07:16,116
And then they struck again.

1457
02:07:20,046 --> 02:07:24,278
l always dream about it in
some grotesque variation.

1458
02:07:25,286 --> 02:07:29,802
Tonight l was one of the watchers,
as if l were at a play.

1459
02:07:32,886 --> 02:07:34,365
Then something happened.

1460
02:07:42,646 --> 02:07:46,036
- What happened? - The
features changed.

1461
02:07:48,206 --> 02:07:49,639
Yeah?

1462
02:07:51,046 --> 02:07:53,162
David, the faces were
yours and mine.

1463
02:08:02,046 --> 02:08:03,365
Good evening, doctor.

1464
02:08:14,886 --> 02:08:16,160
Night, doctor.

1465
02:10:02,566 --> 02:10:05,638
Thank you for bringing
us home, 'capitan. '

1466
02:10:05,806 --> 02:10:09,355
The cuisine and the accommodations
were superb.

1467
02:10:11,806 --> 02:10:13,364
Yeah!

1468
02:10:35,966 --> 02:10:37,285
They've come for me?

1469
02:10:43,646 --> 02:10:45,955
For me, the voyage is over.

1470
02:10:48,566 --> 02:10:50,045
l have here an order..

1471
02:10:51,126 --> 02:10:54,118
..for something that will help
you. Any doctor will accept it.

1472
02:11:12,806 --> 02:11:16,958
Willie.. you try so hard.

1473
02:11:28,886 --> 02:11:32,196
My darling. My love.

1474
02:11:35,366 --> 02:11:39,882
For once, let's kiss
in broad daylight.

1475
02:11:58,286 --> 02:11:59,639
Bye.

1476
02:13:58,115 --> 02:14:02,108
l think we ought to be able to
reach Bremerhaven by Thursday morning.

1477
02:14:07,475 --> 02:14:10,785
Willie, you're drinking
up my best cognac.

1478
02:14:11,795 --> 02:14:15,629
Not that l mind, but that isn't the
thing you should be doing, is it?

1479
02:14:16,115 --> 02:14:17,867
You shouldn't be doing this.

1480
02:14:20,115 --> 02:14:23,994
l know you're still thinking about
her. She'll be all right.

1481
02:14:25,035 --> 02:14:28,550
By now l.. l'll guarantee she's
found someone to help her.

1482
02:14:28,635 --> 02:14:31,547
- Woman like that always
finds someone. - Shut up!

1483
02:14:49,875 --> 02:14:51,024
Willie.

1484
02:14:52,635 --> 02:14:56,105
That's a hell of a way to
waste good brandy, Willie.

1485
02:14:57,555 --> 02:15:00,547
When l think of the things
l've seen on this ship..

1486
02:15:01,035 --> 02:15:03,549
The stupid cruelties. The vanities.

1487
02:15:03,795 --> 02:15:07,185
We talk about values?
There's no values.

1488
02:15:07,715 --> 02:15:10,183
The dung we base our lives on.

1489
02:15:11,195 --> 02:15:14,790
She looked into the garbage dump.
She did something about it.

1490
02:15:15,595 --> 02:15:17,984
And we are the intelligent,
civilized people..

1491
02:15:18,075 --> 02:15:20,111
..who carry out orders we are given.

1492
02:15:20,395 --> 02:15:22,113
No matter what they may be.

1493
02:15:24,635 --> 02:15:27,547
Our biggest mission in life
is to avoid being fools.

1494
02:15:31,195 --> 02:15:33,550
And we wind up being the
biggest fools of all.

1495
02:15:34,635 --> 02:15:36,193
Why didn't l go?

1496
02:15:43,035 --> 02:15:44,468
Come in.

1497
02:15:45,795 --> 02:15:47,990
Herr doctor, Frau Lutz
wants to see you.

1498
02:15:48,075 --> 02:15:50,191
She say's her daughter Elsa
is not feeling well.

1499
02:15:51,715 --> 02:15:52,864
l'm coming.

1500
02:15:53,995 --> 02:15:56,190
To hell with them, Willie.
You rest here.

1501
02:15:56,275 --> 02:15:58,550
You don't look well. You should
see the way you look.

1502
02:16:14,115 --> 02:16:16,106
That is exactly what l mean.

1503
02:16:20,875 --> 02:16:22,388
- Good evening. - Good evening.
- Good evening.

1504
02:16:22,475 --> 02:16:25,547
- You called me? - Doctor,
can you give Elsa a purge?

1505
02:16:31,195 --> 02:16:33,868
Take two of those before you retire.

1506
02:16:34,195 --> 02:16:36,868
Doctor, aren't you going
to take her temperature?

1507
02:16:45,475 --> 02:16:47,193
l think he's been drinking.

1508
02:22:02,555 --> 02:22:07,788
l can just hear you saying, What
has all this to do with us?

1509
02:22:10,275 --> 02:22:11,549
Nothing.

